      <title>当资本进入紧急状态时，谋杀案在秘鲁有记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/murders-hit-record-in-peru-as-capital-enters-state-of-emergency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁于2025年正面临其今年最致命的开始，政府在全国首都施加了紧急状态，试图将罪犯拒之门外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/murders-hit-record-in-peru-as-capital-enters-state-of-emergency</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 13:01:30 GMT</pubDate>
