    <item>
      <title>特朗普律师在委内瑞拉驱逐出境中使法官处于黑暗之中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-lawyers-keep-judge-in-dark-on-venezuelan-deportation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府律师挑衅地辩护唐纳德·特朗普总统驱逐了数百名涉嫌委内瑞拉帮派成员，并拒绝向法官提供信息，他说他需要确定政府是否忽略了他的命令，以将飞机转回美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-lawyers-keep-judge-in-dark-on-venezuelan-deportation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 23:39:30 GMT</pubDate>
